    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kaskade 是一款极简策略游戏，专注于连接不断演变的投递网络。它旨在让你进入心流状态，并以最精简的工具集来描绘画面。   \\n\\n在试玩版中游玩 Kaskade 的前两章！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/b2cb90f9e3d52d4989979faa22a8d544.poster.avif?t=1740603457\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/b2cb90f9e3d52d4989979faa22a8d544.webm?t=1740603457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/b2cb90f9e3d52d4989979faa22a8d544.mp4?t=1740603457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在试玩版中，你可以解锁主游戏中的核心能力，在每次游玩之间进行永久升级，并与排行榜上的高分进行比较。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/f9795112654dc49c643daee175a74597.poster.avif?t=1740603457\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/f9795112654dc49c643daee175a74597.webm?t=1740603457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/f9795112654dc49c643daee175a74597.mp4?t=1740603457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >将输入端与相同颜色的输出端连接来获取点数。使用点数解锁新能力。利用这些新能力让你更高效地管理网络。重复以上步骤。  \\n\\n永久死亡！错误操作过多就会导致游戏结束！游戏没有存档系统，但在每次游玩之间会有 Roguelite 式的进度保留。  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/0894e47d6980bd3c9173e065968517e6.poster.avif?t=1740603457\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/0894e47d6980bd3c9173e065968517e6.webm?t=1740603457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3334730/extras/0894e47d6980bd3c9173e065968517e6.mp4?t=1740603457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在普通和困难难度下游玩主游戏的前两章。 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >禅意的解谜体验或充满策略性的 Roguelite 挑战</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可解锁的关键能力（Jump、Double Jump、Switch、Pause）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >可购买的增益与升级，以应对越来越多的投递</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >色盲模式（投递有清晰标签）</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >支持鼠标和键盘（不推荐使用游戏手柄）</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
